Solution: Scanning sequences to predict transcription factor binding sites

Jacques van Helden

2016-02-09

  • Collection of binding sites
  • Getting the matrix and its consensus
  • Scanning all promoters with the consensus

Collection of binding sites

  • Results of the query “AraC” in RegulonDB
  • Find the section ‘Alignment and PSSM for AraC TFBSs’ to the AraC record in RegulonDB.

  • AraC aligned sites in ‘multi’ format

  • Conversion of site sequences from multi to fasta

convert-seq  -i AraC_sites.multi -from multi -to fasta -o AraC_sites.fa
  • AraC aligned sites in ‘fasta’ format

Getting the matrix and its consensus

  • AraC matrix in tab-delimited format
  • AraC consensus computed by convert-matrix: tatGgaytwwycyGCyr

Scanning all promoters with the consensus
